        <div class="px-5 pb-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700/90 dark:text-slate-300/90">
          <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Guests arrive prepared; fewer “how to find us” calls.</p>
          <p><strong>When it fires:</strong> Immediately on booking + D-1 reminder (time-boxed).</p>
          <p><strong>Experience:</strong> Directions, parking/jetty info, ID upload, ETA confirm in one tap.</p>
          <p><strong>Tags:</strong> <em>pre_info_sent</em>, <em>id_ok</em>, <em>eta_ok</em>.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 2) Check-in coordination -->
      <details class="group mt-4 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-white/30 dark:ring-slate-800/50 bg-white/25 dark:bg-slate-900/20 backdrop-blur">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none p-5 flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="font-semibold">2) Check-in coordination & reminders</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 group-open:hidden">Show</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 hidden group-open:inline">Hide</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-5 pb-5 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700/90 dark:text-slate-300/90">
          <p>Guests adjust arrival time; late arrival path offers alternate windows.</p>
          <p>Tags: <em>checkin_nudge</em>, <em>late_flag</em>, <em>window_changed</em>.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- 3) Upsells -->
      <details class="group mt-4 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-white/30 dark:ring-slate-800/50 bg-white/25 dark:bg-slate-900/20 backdrop-blur">
